This Agreement is made between TechEdge Analytics Pvt. Ltd. and Horizon Capital Advisors.
Each party agrees to maintain confidentiality of proprietary information and shall not disclose it
to any third party without prior written consent. The Agreement shall be governed by the laws of India.
